title: Frieze, 1950–58
description: a) Vertical bands of dark and light blue printed with copper-colored dots and stylized flowers in brown flock alternate with a continuously linked leaf pattern on a light blue ground. On margin: Made in Paris, R C a Paris, 149; b) Frieze of same design as above, overlaid with flocked leaf and flower designs with blue, copper-colored and green border above. Dado repeats border above.

tombstone.epitaph:
Frieze, 1950–58.
1950–58. Machine-printed, flocked. Gift of Jessup, Inc.. 1958-115-41-a,b.
